Sample Data for Package Examples

Source: R/data.R
sample_data.Rd

This dataset contains sample data used for demonstrating examples in the package.

Usage

sample_data

Format

A data frame with 100 observations and 68 variables:

Sample.Type

A factor indicating the type of sample (Type1, Type2, Type3).

Sample.Identification

A character vector specifying sample identification (ID1, ID2, ...).

Gender

A factor indicating gender (Female, Male).

Age

An integer indicating age.

Sample.Description

A factor specifying sample description (DLB, msAD, miAD, HC).

Submission.Name

A factor specifying submission name (plate1, plate2).

Material

A factor indicating material (serum, sample).

Apoe.Genotype

A factor indicating Apoe genotype (Apoe1, Apoe2, Apoe3, Apoe4).
